name: White Crystal Pacha
description: An easy staple- The PACHA range is designed for everyday wear and to suit everyone. Made from coral, timber, howlite beads and features a crystal pendant and white tassel.

name: The Zodiac Necklaces
description:
Fluro strand star sign necklace, silver zodiac tube bead comes with a special charm.



Charms are chosen at random, if you feel strongly about a certain charm (disk, elephant, dove) please put it in the notes at checkout :)

name: The Wrap Me Up

Limited edition bracelet. A wrap style bracelet, designed to create a real statement on your wrist. Made with spikes, wooden beads and glass beads.

ONLY A FEW OF EACH! 

All handmade by Alexandra Redmond.

Available in Rose gold, Gold and Silver.

The Pacha necklace with an amazing addition - A limited edition Amber pendant. Only 5 available all up! Bright magenta contrasts wonderfully against the orange tassel!

name: The Holiday

description:
The Anouk earrings are really something special. Designed for the inner boho glam girl, these bright tribal earrings feature burnt orange tassels and vintage cloisonne beads. These beads are rare and you definately wont find a pair of earrings like this again. Most importantly they are lightweight and easy to wear!

Limited Edition.

name: The Lucia

name: The Island
description:
Awesome lime green necklace, simple in style yet powerful in a statement. The Island would work beautifully on a printed summer dress, or as a burst of colour in a monochrome styling.

name: The Freedom Anklet
description:
These 'Freedom' anklets are a MUST HAVE for summer. Wear one on each ankle for a perfect festival accessory or just one for everyday summer use. 
Made with pom poms, mini tassels, silver coins and silver beads - each one is slightly different which is the beauty of a fully handmade product. Receiving something special which was made especially for you.

Perfect for gifts for someone you love or a special treat for yourself.

name: The Disco Nights

Inspired by pattern and colour, this piece is bound for glory! So versatile and unique, the 'Disco Nights' is easy to wear and adds creativity to any outfit.

* PLEASE NOTE- The spacer bars have changed and are now whiter *

name: The Electric Crystal

name: The Dreamer

Take the Traveller Bracelet away to forge your own memories and stories.

Outfit by : Tigerlily

name: The Rio
description:
The Rio has to be one of the funnest necklaces around. Adds colour, contrast and interest to any outfit. Wear with block colour to work with the necklace or keep it simple in white or black.
Comes in two different colour ways. Pink and Orange or Green and Purple. All handmade - Please allow up to 5 days before shipping.

name: The Zulu
description:
Vintage coins and patterned ceramic beads.
I made this a one off, and keep it and have worn it all the time! So i decided to find more patterned beads and make it more permanent:)
So easy to wear and makes any outfit a stand out.
All handmade - Please allow up to 5 days before shipping.

name: The Lotus Pendant 001
description:
Stunning large purple agate slice pendant with a gold and blood red crystal feature. Each one is a one off style, no two the same. 
Comes with either a gold chain or white leather. 
Pendant measures approx 7.5cm across and 8cm down. Total length of necklace 50cm long. 
All handmade. 

Purple Agate is a crystal of dreams, intuition, and luxury. Agate's most noticeable properties overall are balancing, grounding, protection and calming. It is also known as a good luck stone.
